Dialog: {
	// FrostDwarf: Once upon a time, there were more of us in this village. A whole kind of dwarves, but after the snowmen attack, we were doomed, one of us wanders around the world, the other is in the central city, I sit here and live life alone
	// FrostDwarf2: I wonder how the {0} lives there, in warm, pleasant conditions
	// CityDwarf: Have you heard that there is a ruined village with a lonely dwarf in the Tundra? That was a long story
	// CityDwarf2: I wonder how the {0} lives there, in cold, unpleasant conditions
}

